##  Applications
- Structural Health Monitoring (SHM)  
- Aerospace engineering  
- Mechanical system failure prediction  
- Digital twin systems  



##  Limitations
- Limited to 2D crack modeling  
- Single material (Aluminum 2024-T3)  
- Constant loading conditions  



##  Future Work
- Extend to 3D crack modeling  
- Multi-material systems  
- Real-time deployment in digital twins  
- Uncertainty quantification  

